HIERARCHIAL querySelector
Inside query selector we can target a tag or anything


->The property name in javascript can be different from that of class
1.There are no dashes
2.The first letter of second word is capitalised
3.Values are capitalised
Ex:
document.querySelector(".btn").style.backgroundColor="yellow";
